				<text><![CDATA[Note:-1) A CPHEEO./BIS Std - Desirable limit. B.CPHEEO/BIS Std - Permissible limit in the absence of bealternative source. 2) Results of Chemical Examination expressed in mg/L. 3)Electrical conductivity expressed in micro mho/cm. 4). No unit for pH. 5). C&C-Colourless and Clear. 6). This report refers only to the sample actually subjected to measurements. 7) This report shall not be reproduced, except in full, unless written permission for the same has been from the]]></text>
